out?

00:48:54.190 --> 00:48:55.190
&gt;&gt; Susan Barry: Yeah.

00:48:55.190 --> 00:48:56.190
And that's been a very controversial subject.

00:48:56.190 --> 00:49:01.020
But they've now found areas in the brain that
