&gt;&gt; Susan Barry: Yeah.

00:49:45.330 --> 00:49:46.550
No, it's not.

00:49:46.550 --> 00:49:47.550
Yeah?

00:49:47.550 --> 00:49:51.670
&gt;&gt; male#9: So, it seems like--Iím just assuming
