00:58:31.490 --> 00:58:32.490
Right?

00:58:32.490 --> 00:58:36.030
If you combine both eyes, you've got a wider
visual field.

00:58:36.030 --> 00:58:40.400
And so, then you are able-.

00:58:40.400 --> 00:58:41.510
Then you have a wider visual field.

00:58:41.510 --> 00:58:49.540
So the fact is then you might see more peripherally
