01:04:12.100 --> 01:04:13.710
there's a light on the court, and-

01:04:13.710 --> 01:04:14.710
&gt;&gt;Susan Barry: Oh.

01:04:14.710 --> 01:04:15.710
I see what you're saying.

01:04:15.710 --> 01:04:16.710
You're getting better.

01:04:16.710 --> 01:04:17.710
Yeah.

01:04:17.710 --> 01:04:22.070
My guess would be because the light is coming
